Package: fig2aheatmap
Title: Reproduce Figure 2A Heatmap from Yeast Cell-Cycle Data
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Sandrine",
           family = "Caburet",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "sandrine.caburet@example.org")
Description: Reproducible tools to recreate a Figure 2A-like heatmap from the
    published supplementary ranking table of periodic Saccharomyces cerevisiae
    genes. The package reads the supplementary Excel file, filters genes using
    LS_cutoff and Figure2A_order_peaktime, computes per-gene z-scores, exports
    the processed matrix, and generates a publication-style heatmap.
